dc_description_s: U.S. Highways represents the major and minor highways of the United States. These include Interstates, US Highways, State Highways, major roads, and minor roads. This dataset is a subset of the Streets dataset. It contains all Class 1, 2, and 3 road segments plus any other roads segments necessary to provide network connectivity for the Class_Rte field.
